{"tid":422743,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"今日見到有個呀婆受報應","createTime":"2017-10-03T10:38:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-03T18:38:53.000Z","uid":80396,"like":2,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"6e5a2e185f5ecaecc51710f69789caba6f731baa","tid":422743,"uid":80396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T10:38:33.000Z","msg":"話說今日去釣魚，果度係碼頭有條樓梯果D<br />\n有個呀姐帶左個9歲既細路去釣魚，同場仲有個釣魚呀婆同埋我。<br />\n呀姐：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 細路：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呀婆：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：拿條線震喇，快D拉啦有魚喇！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：哦！好呀！(中左條雞泡魚)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />： 嘩嘩好開心呀有魚喇！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：(細細聲)車，雞泡仔食死你呀。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：(心諗)洗唔洗呀細路仔都串<br />\n過左陣<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：我又有魚喇係泥鯭呀！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />： (細細聲)咁細條比我都掉左去呀。<br />\n我正想出聲果時，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 中左條泥鯭<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：車，至憎D泥鯭仔浪費我D餌<br />\n三秒後<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唉呀！</span><br />\n<br />\n我一睇，個呀婆就比條泥鯭吉到應一應<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：嘰！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n結果望住佢用口啜個傷口，一路啜一路叫好痛一路執野走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57b71d964de7812aa2f1ca12289d6f32c6b4937f","tid":422743,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T10:39:44.000Z","msg":"?"},{"pid":"e70c4133b2c2b8ab686cdc974be4b87ac73a3d18","tid":422743,"uid":31545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T10:59:54.000Z","msg":"你點知個細路9歲？你就係個細路"},{"pid":"ec816fd0ca1832adb659c8f28299eeca0c75caaf","tid":422743,"uid":119993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T11:12:07.000Z","msg":"1999"},{"pid":"17e871f939dce6ab83bb5e3622ec45ae7a2f5731","tid":422743,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T11:14:15.000Z","msg":"?"},{"pid":"e4a79c755ead67fc37f5441ae8e83d6defc855a3","tid":422743,"uid":97451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T11:15:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0473ca7aff53a11d52feb850fddaf8c494fb85ba","tid":422743,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T11:30:11.000Z","msg":"關於泥鯭的傳聞，現請來布袋澳水上人布有輝為大家解答。<br />\n<br />\n【泥鯭有幾多種？】<br />\n主要分深水泥鯭及淺水泥鯭，前者比較大條，可重至兩、三斤，有鱗；淺水泥鯭則較細條，無魚鱗，一般肉質較滑及帶甜。<br />\n【泥鯭吃屎？】<br />\n以前避風塘有好多泥鯭，那裏的洗手間會將排泄物直接排出大海，泥鯭是雜食魚，見到海面上有異物，便會成群追出去吃屎，所以好多人稱為「食屎泥鯭」。通常會在岸邊或碼頭見到，因為牠們吃坑渠水大，所以又稱為「坑渠泥鯭」。<br />\n【水上人點煮泥鯭？】<br />\n水上人不喜歡落果皮或其他多餘的調味料，怕搶走泥鯭本身的甜味，他們喜歡吃原味，會做油鹽水泥鯭，可配榨菜，先煎後放湯煮，或者做鹹鮮。<br />\n【點分坑渠泥鯭？】<br />\n避風塘捉到的泥鯭會較淺色，因為牠們不吃海草，顏色會較白和較瘦。以前海水污染嚴重，因牠們吃過污糟食物，肚內容易生蟲，所以以前有一排好少人吃泥鯭。<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/supplement/20170510/56671248\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fsupplement%2F20170510%2F56671248&d=2IMsTC82ZZRjUYub15B0n5WUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=62ab923b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fsupplement%2F20170510%2F56671248&h=178b838e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/supplement/20170510/56671248</a>"},{"pid":"6fd96304ef7e238fcd7450a4e7f03206d440d52b","tid":422743,"uid":33190,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T11:34:02.000Z","msg":"唔覺個啊婆有幾大問題<br />\n唔係恭恭敬敬，但起碼句句事實<br />\n<br />\n反而樓主你中文又唔掂，小小事都mean成咁，好心你la"},{"pid":"6f03c5be06f1b4691bd1e9b6323218d4a89444d6","tid":422743,"uid":64601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T12:23:10.000Z","msg":"on9呀婆，想從小灌輸失敗主義俾細路。"},{"pid":"2dbdf0d17d284faf1d33879be6f91136f499de08","tid":422743,"uid":67840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T18:38:53.000Z","msg":"tldr"}]}